<main>
  <!-- TL;DR comparative -->
  <section class="ev-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ev-section__tag wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}Quick answer{% else %}Resposta rápida{% endif %}</div>
      <h2 class="ev-section__title wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}Each tool covers a different layer{% else %}Cada ferramenta cobre uma camada diferente{% endif %}</h2>
      <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
          <div style="background:rgba(0,224,163,.06);border:1px solid rgba(0,224,163,.25);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;height:100%;">
            <h4 style="color:#00e0a3;">SAST</h4>
            <p style="font-size:.85rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);">{% if lang == "en" %}Static Application Security Testing{% else %}Análise Estática{% endif %}</p>
            <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Reads your <strong>source code</strong> without running it. Finds SQL injection, insecure deserialization, hardcoded secrets, unsafe APIs.{% else %}Lê seu <strong>código-fonte</strong> sem executá-lo. Encontra SQL injection, desserialização insegura, secrets hardcoded, uso de APIs inseguras.{% endif %}</p>
            <p style="font-size:.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);margin-top:14px;"><strong>{% if lang == "en" %}Stage:{% else %}Momento:{% endif %}</strong> {% if lang == "en" %}IDE + pull request{% else %}IDE + pull request{% endif %}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
          <div style="background:rgba(0,224,163,.06);border:1px solid rgba(0,224,163,.25);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;height:100%;">
            <h4 style="color:#00e0a3;">DAST</h4>
            <p style="font-size:.85rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);">{% if lang == "en" %}Dynamic Application Security Testing{% else %}Análise Dinâmica{% endif %}</p>
            <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Attacks your <strong>running application</strong>, like an external hacker. Finds XSS, auth flaws, misconfig, IDOR, broken business logic.{% else %}Ataca sua <strong>aplicação rodando</strong>, como um hacker externo. Encontra XSS, falhas de auth, misconfig, IDOR, lógica quebrada.{% endif %}</p>
            <p style="font-size:.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);margin-top:14px;"><strong>{% if lang == "en" %}Stage:{% else %}Momento:{% endif %}</strong> {% if lang == "en" %}Staging / pre-prod{% else %}Staging / pré-prod{% endif %}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
          <div style="background:rgba(0,224,163,.06);border:1px solid rgba(0,224,163,.25);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;height:100%;">
            <h4 style="color:#00e0a3;">SCA</h4>
            <p style="font-size:.85rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);">{% if lang == "en" %}Software Composition Analysis{% else %}Análise de Dependências{% endif %}</p>
            <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Maps your <strong>open-source dependencies</strong> and cross-references with CVE/NVD. Finds vulnerable libraries, incompatible licenses, transitive risks.{% else %}Mapeia as <strong>dependências open-source</strong> e cruza com CVE/NVD. Encontra libs vulneráveis, licenças incompatíveis, riscos transitivos.{% endif %}</p>
            <p style="font-size:.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);margin-top:14px;"><strong>{% if lang == "en" %}Stage:{% else %}Momento:{% endif %}</strong> {% if lang == "en" %}Build + continuous{% else %}Build + contínuo{% endif %}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tabela comparativa -->
  <section class="ev-section ev-section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ev-section__tag wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}Side-by-side{% else %}Lado a lado{% endif %}</div>
      <h2 class="ev-section__title wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}What each tool really finds (and misses){% else %}O que cada ferramenta realmente encontra (e deixa passar){% endif %}</h2>
      <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
          <div style="overflow-x:auto;">
            <table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);">
              <thead>
                <tr style="background:rgba(0,224,163,.1);">
                  <th style="padding:14px;text-align:left;color:#00e0a3;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);">{% if lang == "en" %}Vulnerability{% else %}Vulnerabilidade{% endif %}</th>
                  <th style="padding:14px;text-align:center;color:#00e0a3;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);">SAST</th>
                  <th style="padding:14px;text-align:center;color:#00e0a3;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);">DAST</th>
                  <th style="padding:14px;text-align:center;color:#00e0a3;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);">SCA</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);">
                <tr><td style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);">SQL Injection</td><td style="text-align:center;">✅</td><td style="text-align:center;">✅</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td></tr>
                <tr><td style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);">XSS</td><td style="text-align:center;">⚠️</td><td style="text-align:center;">✅</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td></tr>
                <tr><td style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);">Broken Authentication</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td><td style="text-align:center;">✅</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td></tr>
                <tr><td style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);">IDOR / Broken Access Control</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td><td style="text-align:center;">✅</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td></tr>
                <tr><td style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);">Hardcoded secrets</td><td style="text-align:center;">✅</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td></tr>
                <tr><td style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);">Log4Shell (CVE-2021-44228)</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td><td style="text-align:center;">⚠️</td><td style="text-align:center;">✅</td></tr>
                <tr><td style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);">{% if lang == "en" %}Vulnerable transitive dep{% else %}Dependência transitiva vulnerável{% endif %}</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td><td style="text-align:center;">✅</td></tr>
                <tr><td style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);">{% if lang == "en" %}Incompatible license (GPL){% else %}Licença incompatível (GPL){% endif %}</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td><td style="text-align:center;">✅</td></tr>
                <tr><td style="padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);">{% if lang == "en" %}Insecure deserialization{% else %}Desserialização insegura{% endif %}</td><td style="text-align:center;">✅</td><td style="text-align:center;">⚠️</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td></tr>
                <tr><td style="padding:12px;">{% if lang == "en" %}Business logic flaw{% else %}Falha de lógica de negócio{% endif %}</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td><td style="text-align:center;">⚠️</td><td style="text-align:center;">—</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size:.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);margin-top:14px;">✅ {% if lang == "en" %}detects{% else %}detecta{% endif %} · ⚠️ {% if lang == "en" %}partial detection{% else %}detecção parcial{% endif %} · — {% if lang == "en" %}blind spot{% else %}ponto cego{% endif %}</p>
          <p style="margin-top:18px;"><strong>{% if lang == "en" %}Conclusion:{% else %}Conclusão:{% endif %}</strong> {% if lang == "en" %}no single tool covers 100%. Using only SAST leaves logic flaws exposed. Using only DAST misses hardcoded secrets. Using only SCA misses your own code. You need the three layers.{% else %}nenhuma ferramenta sozinha cobre 100%. Usar só SAST deixa lógica exposta. Usar só DAST ignora secrets. Usar só SCA ignora seu próprio código. Precisa das três camadas.{% endif %}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pipeline integrado -->
  <section class="ev-section bg-overly-img">
    <div class="container overlay-content">
      <div class="ev-section__tag wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}Practical pipeline{% else %}Pipeline prático{% endif %}</div>
      <h2 class="ev-section__title wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}How to integrate the three in CI/CD without slowing delivery{% else %}Como integrar os três no CI/CD sem travar entregas{% endif %}</h2>
      <div class="ev-delivery-grid">
        <div class="ev-delivery-card wow fadeInUp">
          <div class="ev-delivery-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-code"></i></div>
          <h4>1. IDE / Pre-commit</h4>
          <p>{% if lang == "en" %}SAST + secret scanning running locally. Budget: &lt; 10 seconds per save. Goal: block critical issues before commit.{% else %}SAST + secret scanning rodando localmente. Orçamento: &lt; 10s por save. Objetivo: bloquear crítico antes do commit.{% endif %}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ev-delivery-card wow fadeInUp">
          <div class="ev-delivery-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-code-branch"></i></div>
          <h4>2. Pull Request</h4>
          <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Incremental SAST (changed files) + SCA on new dependencies. Budget: &lt; 3 minutes. Break build only on new critical finding.{% else %}SAST incremental (arquivos alterados) + SCA em dependências novas. Orçamento: &lt; 3 min. Quebra build só em crítico novo.{% endif %}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ev-delivery-card wow fadeInUp">
          <div class="ev-delivery-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-hammer"></i></div>
          <h4>3. Build / CI</h4>
          <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Full SAST + full SCA on the main branch. Budget: &lt; 15 minutes. Results sent to the vulnerability backlog.{% else %}SAST completo + SCA completo no branch principal. Orçamento: &lt; 15 min. Resultado vai para o backlog de vulnerabilidades.{% endif %}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ev-delivery-card wow fadeInUp">
          <div class="ev-delivery-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-vial"></i></div>
          <h4>4. Staging</h4>
          <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Scheduled DAST (1–2×/week) + authenticated API scan. Budget: overnight window. Don't block deploy; feed the backlog.{% else %}DAST agendado (1–2×/semana) + scan autenticado de APIs. Orçamento: janela noturna. Não bloqueia deploy; alimenta backlog.{% endif %}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ev-delivery-card wow fadeInUp">
          <div class="ev-delivery-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i></div>
          <h4>5. Produção</h4>
          <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Continuous SCA (new CVEs on deployed artifacts) + external DAST monitoring. Alert on every new CVSS ≥ 7.{% else %}SCA contínuo (novas CVEs em artefatos deployados) + monitoramento DAST externo. Alerta a cada nova CVE CVSS ≥ 7.{% endif %}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ev-delivery-card wow fadeInUp">
          <div class="ev-delivery-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i></div>
          <h4>6. {% if lang == "en" %}Governance{% else %}Governança{% endif %}</h4>
          <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Single backlog (not 3 silos), correlated duplicate findings, risk-based prioritization and MTTR by severity.{% else %}Backlog único (não 3 silos), correlação entre achados duplicados, priorização por risco e MTTR por severidade.{% endif %}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

